system.effect:
Trigger - The user hits with a Move with the Five Strike keyword or Population Bomb

Effect: The Triggering Move automatically hits 5 Times, or if its Population Bomb hits 5 + "1 Five-Strike roll" times.

Bonus: This Pokemon counts as an ally (or itself twice) for the use of moves and abilities that would count adjacent allies and counts. (Teamwork, Beat Up, Pack Hunt, Etc.)
